---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import AdSlot from "../components/AdSlot.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="AdSense setup" description="AdSense-ready placement documentation for EdgeIntellab.">
  <main class="section">
    <div class="section-heading">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Monetization</span>
        <h1>AdSense setup</h1>
        <p>Google AdSense publisher verification is configured for EdgeIntellab. Auto Ads can be managed from the AdSense dashboard.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="doc-panel">
        <h2>Configured zones</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Header ads between primary content sections.</li>
          <li>Sidebar ads on article and project detail layouts.</li>
          <li>In-article ads after the main article body.</li>
          <li>Footer ads before the global footer.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="doc-panel">
        <h2>Implementation note</h2>
        <p>The publisher script is loaded from <code>src/layouts/BaseLayout.astro</code> on public pages. Add individual slot IDs to <code>src/components/AdSlot.astro</code> when manual ad units are created in AdSense.</p>
      </div>
      <AdSlot variant="sidebar" />
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
